mindmap
  root((GridWatch<br/>for Logistics))
    Foundation
      4 Toronto data sources
      Conflict detection engine
      Spatial + temporal intelligence
      Role-aware dashboards
    Pain Points
      Where is my cargo right now
      Route blocked, no backup plan
      Unknown road / infra conditions
      Cargo issue mid-route
    The Fix
      Predictive conflict alerts
      Dynamic reroute suggestions
      Live construction/utility/transit feed
      Telemetry partner integration (future)
    Value Delivered
      Fewer delays
      Lower fuel cost
      Better SLA compliance
      Fewer dispatcher hours wasted
    Monetization
      Per-fleet SaaS subscription
      TMS/API integration fee
      Enterprise control tower license
      Agentic sandbox premium tier
